<div class="col-12 col-xl-4">
    <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-header pb-0 p-3">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-8 d-flex align-items-center">
                    <h6 class="mb-0">Profil Bilgileri</h6>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 text-end">
                    <a href="/Member/Profile/Index">
                        <i class="fas fa-user-edit text-secondary text-sm" data-bs-toggle="tooltip" data-bs-placement="top" title="Profili Düzenle"></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body p-3">
            <p class="text-sm">
               Traversal rezervasyon üye paneline hoş geldiniz, sol tarafta bulunan menüler üzerinden geçmiş rezarvasyonlarınızı, aktif rezervasyonlarınızı görebilir yeni rezervasyon oluşturabilirsiniz.
            </p>
            <hr class="horizontal gray-light my-4">
            <ul class="list-group">
                <li class="list-group-item border-0 ps-0 pt-0 text-sm"><strong class="text-dark">Ad Soyad:</strong> &nbsp; @ViewBag.username</li>
                <li class="list-group-item border-0 ps-0 text-sm"><strong class="text-dark">Telefon:</strong> &nbsp; @ViewBag.phone</li>
                <li class="list-group-item border-0 ps-0 text-sm"><strong class="text-dark">Mail Adresi:</strong> &nbsp; @ViewBag.mail</li>
                <li class="list-group-item border-0 ps-0 text-sm"><strong class="text-dark">Konum:</strong> &nbsp; Türkiye</li>
                
                <li class="list-group-item border-0 ps-0 pb-0">
                    <strong class="text-dark text-sm">Sosyal Medya:</strong> &nbsp;
                    <a class="mb-0 ps-1 pe-2 py-0 d-inline-block" href="javascript:;" style="color:#3b5998;">
                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M22 12.06C22 6.49 17.52 2 12 2S2 6.49 2 12.06c0 5.02 3.66 9.18 8.44 9.94v-7.03H7.9v-2.91h2.54V9.41c0-2.51 1.49-3.89 3.77-3.89 1.09 0 2.24.2 2.24.2v2.47h-1.26c-1.24 0-1.63.78-1.63 1.58v1.9h2.78l-.44 2.91h-2.34V22c4.78-.76 8.44-4.92 8.44-9.94z" />
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                    <a class="mb-0 ps-1 pe-2 py-0 d-inline-block" href="javascript:;" style="color:#1da1f2;">
                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M23 3a10.9 10.9 0 0 1-3.14 1.53 4.48 4.48 0 0 0-7.86 3v1A10.66 10.66 0 0 1 3 4s-4 9 5 13a11.64 11.64 0 0 1-7 2c9 5 20 0 20-11.5a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-.08-.83A6.13 6.13 0 0 0 23 3z" />
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                    <a class="mb-0 ps-1 pe-2 py-0 d-inline-block" href="javascript:;" style="color:#e1306c;">
                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M7.5 2h9A5.5 5.5 0 0 1 22 7.5v9a5.5 5.5 0 0 1-5.5 5.5h-9A5.5 5.5 0 0 1 2 16.5v-9A5.5 5.5 0 0 1 7.5 2zm0 1.8A3.7 3.7 0 0 0 3.8 7.5v9a3.7 3.7 0 0 0 3.7 3.7h9a3.7 3.7 0 0 0 3.7-3.7v-9a3.7 3.7 0 0 0-3.7-3.7h-9zM12 7a5 5 0 1 1 0 10 5 5 0 0 1 0-10zm0 1.8a3.2 3.2 0 1 0 0 6.4 3.2 3.2 0 0 0 0-6.4zM17.5 6a1 1 0 1 1 0 2 1 1 0 0 1 0-2z" />
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>